    {
      "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8043-a094-ca90af53311b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "KT is a key task in ITS and DKT is one of the state-of-the-art architectures. In this work, the authors expand on DKT by previously assigning learners to different teams with an unsupervised learning technique according to their ability on regular time intervals. Model becomes better at predicting performance in comparison to other State-of-the-art techniques.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1904750c-f3ba-8043-a094-ca90af53311b",
